1:09:40.777 --> 1:09:42.777
[door rattling]

1:10:10.407 --> 1:10:13.408
[dramatic music]

1:11:04.628 --> 1:11:06.160
[glass shatters]

1:11:08.465 --> 1:11:11.466
[clamoring]

1:11:12.702 --> 1:11:14.869
Let the children go!

