1:12:14.097 --> 1:12:16.064
[dramatic music]

1:12:32.515 --> 1:12:35.683
[bell tolling]

1:12:35.685 --> 1:12:38.119
[mellow music]

1:12:40.023 --> 1:12:43.024
[speaking in foreign language]

1:12:44.361 --> 1:12:46.361
Manav: I'm a journalist.

1:12:48.732 --> 1:12:51.032
What happened?

1:12:51.034 --> 1:12:52.867
Three dead bodies.

1:12:54.137 --> 1:12:55.169
His kids too?

1:12:55.171 --> 1:12:58.139
[speaking in foreign language]

1:13:08.385 --> 1:13:10.518
Two small children.

1:13:10.520 --> 1:13:13.488
[speaking in foreign language]

1:13:21.931 --> 1:13:24.932
[man sobbing]

1:13:30.273 --> 1:13:33.408
Graham: Only two things in life
are certain, mate.

1:13:33.410 --> 1:13:35.410
Death and taxes.

1:13:42.786 --> 1:13:44.452
Manav: Maybe someday
you're gonna play for Australia.

1:13:44.454 --> 1:13:47.555
No, I want to play for India.
Like Sachin.

1:13:47.557 --> 1:13:48.756
Manav: But you're
from Australia.

1:13:48.758 --> 1:13:50.425
I'm from dust.

1:14:27.931 --> 1:14:29.897
[car honking]

1:14:31.568 --> 1:14:34.302
Mishra: Manav.
Manav! Stop, stop!

1:14:36.806 --> 1:14:38.506
Where have you been?

1:14:39.943 --> 1:14:41.909
- Manoharpur.
- And?

1:14:46.516 --> 1:14:48.349
Come. Get in.

1:15:01.297 --> 1:15:02.997
He's been murdered.

1:15:04.133 --> 1:15:05.366
Staines?

1:15:07.604 --> 1:15:09.103
Yes.

1:15:09.105 --> 1:15:11.172
Then not murdered.

1:15:11.174 --> 1:15:13.741
He was killed
for converting tribals.

1:15:15.111 --> 1:15:16.310
But, sir, the man was--

1:15:16.312 --> 1:15:18.546
He must have done something.

1:15:18.548 --> 1:15:20.548
Provoked it somehow.

1:15:23.019 --> 1:15:24.886
There's no evidence.

1:15:24.888 --> 1:15:26.888
Find some.

1:15:26.890 --> 1:15:28.289
What?

1:15:28.291 --> 1:15:31.259
Conversions. Inducements.

1:15:32.795 --> 1:15:34.762
People will talk now.

1:15:42.872 --> 1:15:44.238
Banerjee.

1:15:45.642 --> 1:15:49.043
Staines was into conversions.

1:15:49.045 --> 1:15:52.013
I'm not saying
he should have been killed,

1:15:52.015 --> 1:15:56.851
but... actually this sends out
a good message.

1:15:56.853 --> 1:15:59.320
Teaches the Christians a lesson.

1:15:59.322 --> 1:16:02.256
Stops them from converting.

1:16:02.258 --> 1:16:05.092
Think about it.

1:16:05.094 --> 1:16:07.728
We just need to find
some evidence.

1:16:07.730 --> 1:16:11.232
Account books,
money in, money out,

1:16:11.234 --> 1:16:13.768
title deeds.

1:16:13.770 --> 1:16:16.504
Seek and ye shall find.

1:16:17.840 --> 1:16:19.807
What about the boys?

1:16:21.911 --> 1:16:24.412
His sons?

1:16:24.414 --> 1:16:26.414
They killed them also.

1:16:29.686 --> 1:16:32.620
They would have grown up
to convert...

1:16:32.622 --> 1:16:34.956
like their father.

1:16:34.958 --> 1:16:37.158
We have to be strong, Banerjee.

1:16:39.195 --> 1:16:41.896
We must print the truth.

1:16:41.898 --> 1:16:45.066
Staines was not a hero,

1:16:45.068 --> 1:16:46.534
not a martyr.

1:16:46.536 --> 1:16:48.936
Do you know a man
named Mahendra?

1:16:51.074 --> 1:16:52.506
No.

1:17:14.998 --> 1:17:17.999
[singing in foreign language]

1:17:23.306 --> 1:17:26.307
[indistinct chatter]

1:17:28.511 --> 1:17:31.512
[singing continues]

1:18:44.821 --> 1:18:46.087
[sighs]

1:18:48.825 --> 1:18:50.558
Esther: [knocks] Mom?

1:18:50.560 --> 1:18:52.359
[knock on door]

1:18:52.361 --> 1:18:53.661
[sniffles]

1:19:05.408 --> 1:19:08.442
Have you heard something more,
mom?

1:19:08.444 --> 1:19:12.246
No. I'm just--
I just needed a minute.

1:19:15.118 --> 1:19:18.352
All these people coming.
Someone must know something.

1:19:19.555 --> 1:19:21.522
Perhaps, yes.

1:19:25.628 --> 1:19:27.962
Esther: I wish
they could tell us.

1:19:27.964 --> 1:19:31.699
Sweetheart,
[sniffles] come on now.

1:19:32.535 --> 1:19:34.535
No moping about.

1:19:34.537 --> 1:19:37.204
Your dad could walk
through that door any minute.

1:19:37.206 --> 1:19:39.740
[mellow music]

1:19:39.742 --> 1:19:42.643
[chuckles] Alright?

1:19:49.585 --> 1:19:52.353
God's in control
even when we don't understand.

1:19:53.756 --> 1:19:55.055
[sighs]

